    <lb n="1"/>Σουηροῦς Σαραπίωνι 

    <lb n="2"/>καὶ Χαιρήμωνι τοῖς κυρίοις 

    <lb n="3"/>καὶ υἱοῖς πολλὰ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="4"/>πρὸ μὲν πάντων εὔ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">χ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ομ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αι</unclear> ὑμᾶς 

    <lb n="5"/>ὑγιαίνειν καὶ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ιὰ</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">παντὸς ἐ</supplied>ρρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῶσ</supplied>-

    <lb n="6"/>θαι σὺν τῷ ἀδελφῷ <choice><corr>ὑμῶν</corr><sic>ημων</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="7"/>κόμισαι παρὰ τοῦ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἀ</unclear>ν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>διδ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">όν</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear>τος 

    <lb n="8"/>σοι τὸ ἐπιστόλιον τὴν στραγ-

    <lb n="9"/><choice><corr>γίδα</corr><sic>στραγγιδαν</sic></choice> ὡς ἔγραψας καὶ σφραγί-

    <lb n="10"/>δια <num value="4">δ</num> ὡς ἔγραψας.  ἄσπαζε τοὺς 

    <lb n="11"/>φιλοῦντας ἡμᾶς <choice><corr>π<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ά</supplied>ντας</corr><sic>π<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>ντες</sic></choice> <choice><corr>κατ᾽</corr><sic><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">καθ</unclear></sic></choice> ὄνο-

    <lb n="12"/>μα.  παρακαλῶ <choice><corr>ὑμᾶς</corr><sic>ημας</sic></choice> ὑπὸ <choice><corr>χεῖρα</corr><sic>χαιραν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="13"/>μοι γράψαι περὶ τῆς <choice><corr>ὑγιείας</corr><sic>υγιας</sic></choice> ὑμῶν. 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐγὼ γὰρ δυσκόλως <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εὑ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρί</unclear>σκω <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἴ</supplied> 

    <lb n="15"/>τίς μοι γράψῃ.  ἔρρω<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σο</unclear>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

